"Sentinel 6 to main base" said a voice in darkfate's
com link "I register an strange movement in secor
6-4-3..."

"report" Replied Darkfate in his comlink.

"An strange movement is in my sector, boss, it isn't a
eartquake... It seem to be something big, boss!!!! i
need more bots to start a big-mess..."

Darkfate frowns. "You'll get it, soldier, but you
won't shoot until I did the signal..."

"okie dokie" replied the voice

"And" added Darkfate "try to be more formal... we're
warriors not teenagers"

Darkfate cut the comunication and used it again to
call at all his troops "to all... I need you in sector
6-4-3... Scorpyo and blacknighmare in surface... the
others undergroud... Don't shoot until I gave the cue"

"I'll need a form after all" muttered Darkfate while
he typed a buttons
